obj_root_law_sections_4_content:
  string
  line `The repeal by this Act of any enactment shall not affect any Act in which such`
  line `enactment has been applied, incorporated or referred to;`
  line
  line `and this Act shall not affect the validity, invalidity, effect or consequences of anything already`
  line `done or suffered, or any right, title, obligation or liability already acquired, accrued or incurred, or any`
  line `remedy or proceeding in respect thereof, or any release or discharge of or from any debt, penalty,`
  line `obligation, liability, claim or demand, or any indemnity already granted, or the proof of any past act or`
  line thing;
  line
  line `nor shall this Act affect any principle or rule of law, or established jurisdiction, form or course of`
  line `pleading, practice or procedure, or existing usage, custom, privilege, restriction, exemption, office or`
  line `appointment, notwithstanding that the same respectively may have been in any manner affirmed,`
  line `recognised or derived by, in or from any enactment hereby repealed;`
  line
  line `nor shall the repeal by this Act of any enactment provide or restore any jurisdiction, office,`
  line `custom, liability, right, title, privilege, restriction, exemption, usage, practice, procedure or other`
  line `matter or thing not now existing or in force.`
obj_root_law_sections_4_footnotes:
  string
  line
